      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·秦風·005.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">終南.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>終南何有，有條有梅。君子至止，錦衣狐裘。顏如渥丹，其君也哉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>What are there on Chung-nan?
There are white firs and plum trees.
Our prince has arrived at it,
Wearing an embroidered robe over his fox-fur,
And with his countenance rouged as with vermilion.
May he prove a ruler indeed!</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
