      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·秦風·005.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">終南.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>終南何有，有紀有堂。君子至止，黻衣繡裳。佩玉將將，壽考不亡。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>What are there on Chung-nan?
There are nooks and open glades.
Our prince has arrived at it,
With the symbol of distinction embroidered on his lower skirt,
And the gems at his girdle emitting their tinkling.
May long life and an endless name be his?</seg>
      </tuv>
